MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

This is the smallest deployable unit that delivers value:

- gate-530 API server (HTTP/1.1) wrapping Gate530Engine
- JWT signature verification via jose (HS256 + JWKS RS256)
- PostgreSQL evidence/audit persistence with WORM protection
- Ed25519 evidence signing via @ios-plus/evidence-fabric
- Real /ready probe with database connectivity check
- Prometheus-compatible /metrics endpoint
- Admin endpoints for rule CRUD and audit queries
- 15 unit tests for Gate530Engine
- 12 integration tests for HTTP API
- Per-service Dockerfile (multi-stage)
- docker-compose.mvp.yml for local end-to-end
- K8s manifests: Deployment, Service, ConfigMap, Kustomization
- Full API specification (WAVE1_MVP_SPEC.md)

BREAKING CHANGE: packages/gate-530/src/index.ts now exports API modules

Refs: WAVE1_MVP_SPEC.md
