+        <li><strong>Input:</strong> LMS assessment structure (count, type, rubric complexity) + Banner section data (enrollment, modality)</li>
+        <li><strong>Calculation:</strong> Grading Load Index = weighted function of assessments × students × complexity</li>
+        <li><strong>Output:</strong> Dean-level dashboard for support allocation</li>
+        <li><strong>Evidence:</strong> Auditable, formula-driven, no guesswork</li>
+      </ul>
+      <p><strong>Value:</strong> Rational support allocation; fairness as a number</p>
+    `
+  },
+  uc06: {
