+    meta: 'One Dashboard, Ten Programs, Zero Spreadsheets',
+    body: `
+      <p><strong>Buyer-visible outcome:</strong> Programmatic compliance tracking</p>
+      <ul>
+        <li><strong>Tracks:</strong> Accreditor requirements, licensure exam outcomes, outcome thresholds per program</li>
+        <li><strong>Replaces:</strong> 10 disconnected coordinator spreadsheets</li>
+        <li><strong>Alerting:</strong> NCLEX-RN threshold breach detection with early warning</li>
+      </ul>
+      <p><strong>Value:</strong> Prevents $500K program loss by catching threshold drift before breach</p>
