+# ============================================================================
+# IOS+ Platform — ML Jobs (CronJob)
+# ============================================================================
+# Risk scoring (every 6 hours), drift detection (daily), and accreditation
+# load indexing (weekly). Cloud SQL Auth Proxy sidecar for DB writes.
